s no reward for him.\u201d The people found that very difficult, so\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":6859,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/09\/21\/virtues-prayer-parents-jihad\/","url_meta":{"origin":38798,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Virtues: Prayer, goodness to parents, jihad","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"September 21, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Abdullah ibn Mas\u2019ud reported: I asked, \u201cO Messenger of Allah, which deed is best?\u201d The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cPrayer in its proper time.\u201d I asked, \u201cWhat is next?\u201d The Prophet said, \u201cGood treatment of\u00a0your parents.\u201d I said, \u201cWhat is next?\u201d The Prophet said,\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]}],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/38798","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/3712"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=38798"}],"version-history":[{"count":0,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyh